  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 39.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第39课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Am I All Right?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我是否痊愈？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why did Mr. Gilbert",
      "translation": {
        "text": "吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "telephone Dr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "为什么给米灵顿医生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Millington?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "打电话？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "While John Gilbert was in hospital, he asked his doctor to tell him whether his operation had been successful.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "约翰·吉尔伯特住院期间，请医生告诉他手术是否成功。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "But the doctor refused to do so.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "但医生拒绝告诉他。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "The following day, the patient asked for a bedside telephone.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第二天，病人要了一部床头电话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "When he was alone, he telephoned the hospital exchange and asked for Dr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "独处时，他打电话给医院总机，要求接通米灵顿"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Millington.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "医生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "When the doctor answered the phone, Mr. Gilbert",
      "translation": {
        "text": "医生接电话后，吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "said he was inquiring about a certain patient, a Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "说他想询问一位病人的情况，一位"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "Gilbert.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "吉尔伯特先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "He asked if Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他问吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Gilbert's operation had been successful, and the doctor told him that it had been.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "的手术是否成功，医生告诉他手术很成功。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "He then asked when Mr. Gilbert",
      "translation": {
        "text": "接着他又问吉尔伯特先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "would be allowed to go home, and the doctor told him that he would have to stay in hospital for another two weeks.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "什么时候可以回家，医生告诉他还得在医院住两个星期。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "Then Dr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "随后米灵顿"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "Millington asked the caller if he was a relative of the patient.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "医生问打电话的人是否是病人的亲属。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "No, the patient answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“不是，”病人回答，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "I am Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我就是吉尔伯特"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "Gilbert.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先生。”"
      }
    }
  ],
